{"type":null,"faqId":11571,"title":"C8816D  静态IP进行使用WLAN上网","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">点击<b>设置</b><span>-&gt;<b>WLAN</b></span>，点击要连接的热点，在弹出的对话框中，勾选<b>显示高级选项</b>；在<span>IP</span>设置里选择<b>静态</b>，依次填写<b><span>IP</span>地址</b>（大部分设置为<span>192.168.1.***</span>）、<b>网关</b>（大部分都是<span>192.168.1.1</span>）、<b>网络前缀长度</b>和域名（<span>dns</span>地址）即可。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=32880\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">使用<span>WLAN</span>入网络最大的问题就是不能实现免等待连接网络，移动设备连接上路由器之后会获取一个动态的<span>IP</span>地址，比较费时。使用静态<span>IP</span>的进行<span>WLAN</span>上网，就可以实现急速上网。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2354","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398501323000,"seriesProductName":"C8816D","visitedTimes":142,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"C8816D","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}